# Optional. Leave unset for the Pi/TV and the dev server — the frontend talks
# to the same origin (Vite proxies /api + /ws in dev; FastAPI serves them in prod).
# Only set this for a *separate* phone app that points at the Pi directly, e.g.
# VITE_API_BASE=http://compeetah.local:8000
VITE_API_BASE=
